headline: PSE&G Proactively Implements Summer Relief Initiative to Protect Residential Electric Customers from Higher Costs
summary: PSE&G today announced that it is proactively implementing a Summer Relief Initiative to protect qualified residential electric customers from disconnection, while seeking approval from the New Jersey Board of Public Utilities (BPU) to provide New Jerseyans relief on their summer electric bills.
